============================================================
CONFIG REQUIREMENTS
============================================================

Update root `.env.example`:

BILLING_ENABLED=true
BILLING_PROVIDER=mock
BILLING_CURRENCY=USD
BILLING_TRIAL_DAYS=14
BILLING_GRACE_PERIOD_DAYS=7
BILLING_WEBHOOK_SECRET=
BILLING_FAIL_CLOSED=true

STRIPE_ENABLED=false
STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=
STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET=
STRIPE_PRICE_STARTER=
STRIPE_PRICE_PRO=
STRIPE_PRICE_ENTERPRISE=

USAGE_METERING_ENABLED=true
USAGE_ENFORCEMENT_ENABLED=true
USAGE_RESET_MODE=monthly

MARKETPLACE_ENABLED=true
MARKETPLACE_INSTALL_ENABLED=true
MARKETPLACE_REVIEW_REQUIRED=true
PLUGIN_RUNTIME_MODE=sandbox
PLUGIN_ALLOW_EXTERNAL_NETWORK=false
PLUGIN_ALLOW_SECRET_ACCESS=false

ENTERPRISE_LICENSE_ENABLED=true
ENTERPRISE_OFFLINE_LICENSE_ENABLED=true
ENTERPRISE_EXPORT_ENABLED=true
ENTERPRISE_IMPORT_ENABLED=true

WHITE_LABEL_ENABLED=true
DEFAULT_BRAND_NAME=zDash
DEFAULT_BRAND_LOGO_URL=
DEFAULT_BRAND_PRIMARY_COLOR=#7c3aed
DEFAULT_BRAND_ACCENT_COLOR=#22c55e

ONBOARDING_ENABLED=true
CUSTOMER_SUCCESS_ENABLED=true

Rules:

- Mock billing must work without provider secrets.
- Real Stripe mode requires all required Stripe config.
- Billing must fail closed when BILLING_FAIL_CLOSED=true.
- Marketplace plugin runtime must default to sandbox.
- Plugins must not access secrets unless explicitly allowed and reviewed.
- White-label settings must be tenant-scoped.
- Usage metering must be tenant-scoped.
- Enterprise export/import must never include secrets by default.

