============================================================
ENTITLEMENT REQUIREMENTS
============================================================

Create:

backend/app/billing/entitlement_service.py

Methods:

- get_plan_for_org(organization_id) -> BillingPlan
- check_feature(organization_id, feature) -> EntitlementDecision
- check_quota(organization_id, workspace_id, metric, increment=1) -> EntitlementDecision
- require_feature(feature)
- require_quota(metric, increment=1)

Rules:

- Enterprise plan allows custom limits.
- Free plan must be safe and limited.
- If billing is disabled in dev, allow but mark mock/dev mode.
- If billing provider fails and BILLING_FAIL_CLOSED=true, block paid-only features.
- Never bypass tenant isolation.
- Entitlement checks must be used by:
  - backtest run
  - optimization run
  - scheduler job creation
  - content creation
  - marketplace plugin install
  - realtime stream access
  - enterprise export

