Plugin safety:

- No external network by default.
- No secret access by default.
- No live trading actions.
- No real IoT actions.
- No real social posting.
- Plugins can only call allowed internal services.
- Plugins must be tenant-scoped.
- Plugin install requires marketplace entitlement.

