============================================================
DATABASE UPDATES
============================================================

Add SQLAlchemy tables:

- billing_plans
- subscriptions
- usage_records
- invoices
- plugin_manifests
- plugin_installations
- enterprise_licenses
- branding_settings
- export_bundles
- onboarding_checklists

All tenant-scoped where applicable.

Requirements:
- SQLite compatible.
- PostgreSQL compatible.
- Migration/create_all support.
- No raw card data.
- No plaintext license keys.
- No secrets in export bundles by default.

============================================================
API RESPONSE FORMAT
============================================================

All endpoints must use standard response shape:

Success:

{
  "ok": true,
  "data": {},
  "error": null,
  "timestamp": "ISO_DATE"
}

Error:

{
  "ok": false,
  "data": null,
  "error": {
    "code": "ERROR_CODE",
    "message": "Human readable message"
  },
  "timestamp": "ISO_DATE"
}

Required error codes:

- BILLING_PROVIDER_NOT_CONFIGURED
- SUBSCRIPTION_INACTIVE
- PLAN_NOT_FOUND
- FEATURE_NOT_ENTITLED
- QUOTA_EXCEEDED
- PLUGIN_NOT_FOUND
- PLUGIN_NOT_APPROVED
- PLUGIN_SAFETY_BLOCKED
- LICENSE_INVALID
- EXPORT_NOT_ALLOWED
- TENANT_ACCESS_DENIED

